Price Waterhouse Coopers Indonesia Jobs: Consultant | IT Auditor | Audit Associate
The opportunity of a lifetime in PwC Consulting Indonesia. Build your unique career with PwC Consulting, and become a member of PwC’s South East Asia Consulting. Our diverse professionals bring a wealth of experience from business, government and academia—helping our clients from strategy through execution to close the gap between ideas and results. It is all about you. Your personal and professional development, your achievement, your life long learning, your individuality, and your choices.
Consultant
Requirement
ADVERTISEMENT
Bachelor degree or Master Degree in Environmental Engineering / Industrial Engineering / IT / Accounting / Management with GPA minimum 3.00 out of 4.00
Excellent communication in English, both oral and written.
Strong analytical skill, creative thinking, project management skills.
Teamwork capabilities with strong client orientation drive.
Will be graduated in June 2014 or earlier
Closing date: May 14, 2014
IT Auditor
Requirement
Bachelor degree or Master Degree in Information Technology (IT) / Accounting with GPA minimum 3.00 out of 4.00
Excellent communication in English, both oral and written.
Strong analytical thinking
Teamwork capabilities with strong client orientation drive.
Will be graduated in August 2014 or earlier
Closing date: May 30, 2014
Audit Associate
